## How to Cite and Attribute

### **For the entire framework:**
```
HCV-CARE: Decentralized Model of Care for Hepatitis C and Cardiovascular 
Disease Management in Rohingya Refugee Camps, Cox's Bazar, Bangladesh. 
Version 3.0. Community Partners International, Bangladesh Mission (2026).
https://github.com/CPI-BGD/HCV-CARE
Available under CC BY 4.0 License.
```

### **For specific documents:**
```
[Document Title]. HCV-CARE Framework, Version 3.0. 
Community Partners International, Bangladesh Mission (2026).
https://github.com/CPI-BGD/HCV-CARE
Author: [Original Author if known]
Available under CC BY 4.0 License.
```

### **In HTML/Web:**
```html
<p>This work is licensed under a 
<a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">
Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License</a>.</p>
<p>Based on work by <a href="https://github.com/CPI-BGD/HCV-CARE">
Community Partners International, HCV-CARE Project</a></p>
```

### **In BibTeX (Academic):**
```bibtex
@manual{HCV-CARE2026,
  author = {Islam, Mohammad Ariful and Community Partners International},
  title = {HCV-CARE: Decentralized Model of Care for Hepatitis C and 
           Cardiovascular Disease Management in Refugee Settings},
  version = {3.0},
  year = {2026},
  organization = {Community Partners International, Bangladesh Mission},
  url = {https://github.com/CPI-BGD/HCV-CARE},
  note = {Licensed under CC BY 4.0}
}
```

