## Permitted Uses

✅ **Educational Use**: Use in training programs, schools, universities

✅ **Adaptation**: Modify for your context (add your logo, translate, adapt for other settings)

✅ **Commercial Use**: Can be used for fee-based training or consulting

✅ **Distribution**: Share with others, publish in other formats

✅ **Derivative Works**: Create new materials based on this framework

✅ **Offline Use**: Print, distribute in printed form, use offline

---

## Required Actions

When using, you MUST:

1. **Give Credit**: State that work is based on HCV-CARE framework
2. **Provide License**: Include CC BY 4.0 license statement
3. **Link to Original**: Include link to https://github.com/CPI-BGD/HCV-CARE
4. **Indicate Changes**: If you modified content, clearly indicate what changed

### **Simple Attribution Example**

```
This training material is adapted from the HCV-CARE: Decentralized Model 
of Care Framework (https://github.com/CPI-BGD/HCV-CARE), licensed under 
CC BY 4.0 by Community Partners International, Bangladesh Mission.

This version includes [describe your changes]. [Year, Your Organization]
```

